text: The Anti-White race war is new, isn't it? (Post-1960s as a general leftist commitment.)
Not sure Westerners are quite aware of the degree to which Shanghai does not have this.

On my visits to the Anglosphere I'm always struck by how much profound decivilization is just accepted as inevitable. 
"Shoplifting, I mean, what can you do?"
"Umm, stop shoplifting?"
"But that would be mean, and probably racist."
All of human history until perhaps 50 years ago has understood that criminals have negative value.
So want to see @RokoMijic 's reaction when he sees this.
